(man) 48-YEAR-OLD MALE
INVOLVED IN A HEAD-ON COLLISION

40:48.083 --> 40:51.083
SUSTAINED A DEEP 6-CENTIMETER
LACERATION TO THE LEFT CHEST.

40:51.125 --> 40:54.417
VITALS--B.P., 95 OVER 60,
PULSE 120.

40:54.458 --> 40:56.417
WE'VE GOT A POSSIBLE
SUBCLAVIAN ARTERY INJURY.

40:56.458 --> 40:59.041
WE COULD USE YOUR HELP HERE,
DR. BENNETT.
YEAH.

40:59.083 --> 41:01.542
(Addison) YOU'RE
THE CARDIAC SURGEON ON CALL?
YEAH, I AM.

41:01.583 --> 41:04.041
UH, WHAT ABOUT MAYA?
I WILL BE WITH HER
THE WHOLE TIME.

41:04.083 --> 41:06.917
YOU'LL BE DONE BEFORE SHE'S
EVEN CLOSE TO DELIVERING.
OKAY.

41:06.959 --> 41:08.917
UH, UPDATES EVERY HALF-HOUR?
I PROMISE.

41:08.959 --> 41:10.291
ALL RIGHT. THANK YOU.

41:10.333 --> 41:11.500
(laughs)

